Package: SSPT
Title: Single Sample Pathway Perturbation Testing for RNA-seq 
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Wenjun", "Liu", , "wenjun.liu@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8185-3069"))
Description: A single sample pathway pertrubation testing methods that compute pathway perturbation scores with directionality. The final output can be used to test the significance of pathway perturbation at individual-sample or collective treatment levels.  
